name: Trinket Car Signaling Prank
description:
This app is intended for entertainment purposes only and does not provide true Car Key.
Trinket Car Signaling Prank - this is a game simulation of a joke application where you can play with your phone as a remote control for the car! Do you like cars? Neto car, but we would like to pretend that there is? Then our app for you!
With this application you can turn the sound on this car alarm! Scare your friends! The interface is very simple and easy! Turn on the app and start to joke and play!
Download the game and play everywhere, because it does not require an internet connection!
Warning game joke created for pranks and practical jokes and is absolutely safe for your health!
Thank you for playing our applications! Leave us feedback and we will try to make them even more interesting!
